'''''Zeltrons in Love''''' was a popular [[Holodrama/Legends|holodrama]] series, whose production was financed by the [[Zeltron/Legends|Zeltron]] monarchy to advertise creations of the Zeltron science industry. Characters included [[Jojo (holodrama character)|Jojo]] (a fat [[Devaronian/Legends|Devaronian]] bartender) and [[Derc]] (a Zeltron man).

An episode where Jojo advised Derc to use [[Essence of Zeltros]] to woo [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]], whom he was semi-stalking, was only showed once due to a threatened lawsuit by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]].

